Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.18,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,FESTIVAL DE INVERNO\NCÂMERA ANTIGA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Fala "xis"!\N- Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
